  recipeId: 3
  title: Swiftstep Draught
  totalTimesCrafted: 0
  text: 'A light potion infused with celestial magic that temporarily increases movement
    speed.


    1. Start the fire under the cauldron.

    2. Add either 2 Pumpkins
    or 3 Turnips to the brew.

    3. Add a Moonveil Rose.

    4. Stir exactly 2
    times.


'
